## Nix ignores:
/.direnv
/.envrc

## Hugo specific ignores:
/public
.hugo_build.lock
hugo_stats.json

## Generated Chroma stylesheets (see package.json's generate:chroma script):
/assets/css/chroma-latte.css
/assets/css/chroma-mocha.css

## Self-hosted webfonts (see scripts/fetch-fonts.sh):
/static/fonts

## Generated version info (see scripts/generate-version.sh):
/static/version.json

## Node.js ignores:
/node_modules

## Content ignores:
/content/posts/**/*.hi
/content/posts/**/*.o

## Various ignores:
/tmp
